Package: ajd.sim.bk
Title: Simulation of Affine Jump Diffusions Using Broadie-Kaya Method
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yan-Feng", "Wu", , "yanfengwu13@fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7105-1070"))
Description: Simulate exactly the Heston stochastic volatility model and its 
    affine jump diffusion extensions using the Broadie-Kaya algorithm. 
    The extensions include a) incorporating jumps in the price process, 
    b) adding contemporaneous jumps both in the price and variance processes. 
